{"tid":1148593,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 7 用 Chrome 比 Windows 10 快 5 倍！因 Windows 10 一個保安功能導致！","createTime":"2019-05-10T14:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T12:15:25.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"019a3a1097f1f8a3e8c312f1e6464d77ad4c07fd","tid":1148593,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"很多人也用 Chrome，但有沒有想過在 Windows 10 跑 Chrome 的速度不如 Windows 7？近日瀏覽器 Vivaldi 團隊發現 Windows 10 因為一個安全功能，令 Chromium 核心的瀏覽器（包括 Chrome、Opera 等瀏覽器）速度比 Windows 7 慢。<br />\n<br />\n他們以一個原本在 Windows 7 要 100 分鐘完成的測試，以 Windows 10 進行，結果用了 300 至 360 分鐘才完成。另一組測試，原本在 Windows 7 進行只需 20 分鐘的測試，在 Windows 10 更要 100 分鐘才完成。<br />\n<br />\nVivaldi 團隊發現 Windows 7 運作瀏覽器的速度比 Windows 10 快，於是主動聯絡 Chromium 團隊尋求協助，結果發現原因竟然來自 Windows 10 自身的 Control Flow Guard (CFG) 功能。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Control Flow Guard 功能早在 Windows 8.1 時已引進 Windows，能夠阻擋攻擊者透過一些漏洞入侵電腦。預設情況下，CFG 功能是會啟動的。而 Chromium 開發者 Bruce Dawson 測試過將 CFG 功能強制關閉，結果速度又回復正常了。<br />\n<br />\n下一代 Microsoft Edge 瀏覽器也將用 Chromium 內核，相信微軟不會故意令它變慢。所以日前微軟已經修正這個問題，並預計會在5月14日的每月更新中推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/05/03/chrome-win7-faster-than-win10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F05%2F03%2Fchrome-win7-faster-than-win10%2F&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=92773326\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/05/03/chrome-win7-faster-than-win10/</a>"},{"pid":"0b107c07fa3482e96fb1d3fe48bb0a8a793da5f0","tid":1148593,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">關閉Windows 10 的 Control Flow Guard (CFG) 功能</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://cck.tw/disabling-control-flow-guard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcck.tw%2Fdisabling-control-flow-guard&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=94186569\" target=\"_blank\">https://cck.tw/disabling-control-flow-guard</a><br />\n<br />\n最近有個消息：Windows 7 用 Chrome 比 Windows 10 快 5 倍，微軟已經修正這個問題，並預計會在5月14日的每月更新中推出。在還沒等到更新前，可以先自行手動停用Control Flow Guard (CFG) 功能，步驟如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cck.tw/wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dis_cfg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcck.tw%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fdis_cfg1.jpg&h=1301eb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cck.tw/wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dis_cfg2-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcck.tw%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fdis_cfg2-1.jpg&h=232dd6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cck.tw/wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dis_cfg3-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcck.tw%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fdis_cfg3-1.jpg&h=ccefbd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cck.tw/wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dis_cfg4-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcck.tw%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fdis_cfg4-1.jpg&h=2e33a6ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"310fd8d330487543870c90b699c553a195fb6c39","tid":1148593,"uid":182113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"18294eedab491237a62453f2d65cc7c52df2cbcc","tid":1148593,"uid":44073,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ce2531c23575f76369edb550134ed0d431d16e9","tid":1148593,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc998c6513f17d471b0e7c0a38486b608f2dfa16","tid":1148593,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T21:26:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1001f6e27c7ded6359342087dea3fe95b7c674a7","tid":114